**distinctDistances A** = {sqDist(p,q) : p,q ∈ A, p ≠ q}

**distanceCount A** = |distinctDistances A|

This counts how many different pairwise distances appear in the point set.

**InGeneralPosition p₁ p₂ p₃ p₄**: No three points are collinear.

This is checked for all 4 triples:
- ¬Collinear ℝ {p₁, p₂, p₃}
- ¬Collinear ℝ {p₁, p₂, p₄}
- ¬Collinear ℝ {p₁, p₃, p₄}
- ¬Collinear ℝ {p₂, p₃, p₄}
